foggy; Cincinnati 66 partly cloudy; Cleveland 66 cloudy; Detroit 62
partly cloudy; Hatteras 72 cloudy; Jacksonville 71 foggy; Key West
83 fair; Knoxville 71 foggy; Macon 71 foggy; Miami 80 fair; New York
77 hazy; Philadelphia 74 foggy; Pittsburgh 65 foggy; Portland, Maine
68 foggy; Richmond 73 foggy; Tampa 77 partly cloudy; Washington,
D.C. 76 foggy.
   _Central: Bismarck 39 fair; Chicago 62 partly cloudy; Denver 41
rain; Des Moines 57 partly cloudy; Fort Worth 74 fair; Indianapolis
66 fair; Kansas City 56 fair; Little Rock 68 foggy; Louisville 70
cloudy; Memphis 72 foggy; Nashville 73 cloudy; New Orleans 77
cloudy; North Platte 44 cloudy; Oklahoma City 66 thunderstorms;
Omaha 54 fair; Rapid City 33 fair; St. Louis 65 fair;
Minneapolis-St. Paul 55 cloudy; Sault Ste. Marie 48 fair; San
Antonio 78 showery.
   _West: Anchorage 55 cloudy; Boise 53 cloudy; Casper 32 cloudy;
Fairbanks 58 cloudy; Great Falls 37 fair; Honolulu 78 fair; Las
