<HEAD>Youth Shot Dead Outside Brooklyn High School</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A high school student was shot and killed outside
a school as classes resumed Monday for the new academic year, the
police said.
   Investigators believed a second youth was injured but he had not
been found, a spokesman said. The shooting happened at 11:15 a.m.
outside Prospect Heights High School in the borough of Brooklyn.
