palladium futures, which make up 5 percent of Nymex volume. It also
did not affect trading at the three other futures exchanges that
share space at the World Trade Center: the Commodity Exchange, the
New York Cotton Exchange, and the Coffee, Sugar &amp; Cocoa Exchange.
