<HEAD>Rockefeller Group Seeking Ways To Raise More Cash</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Rockefeller Group Inc. confirmed Monday it was
seeking ways to raise more cash for the family members who are
majority shareholders, after a published report indicated part of
the firm could be up for sale by month's end.
   The company's management has been authorized by the board of
